Rating: 3
The salad really makes this dish. I let the shallots soak for five minutes with the vinegar in a mortar and pestle and then added a wedge of the pear and blended it into the vinaigrette before adding the oil and honey. Overall, it was a nice alternative to heavier sides that usually get offered with steak. We'll do this one again.

