Rating: 4
Cannot beat a good, simple steak paired with a fantastic salad. Loved the light dressing. I used white wine vinegar--that's what I had on hand and it worked well. Added toasted walnuts for some crunch. Did not have comice pears so I used Bosc. Apples would be great too. Craved same salad next day--so good!